Chinchompas=

By using [[Chinchompa (weapon)|chinchompas]], one can kill [[Kree'arra]] quickly even if they are soloing, though it is also expensive. <br/>
To use this method, stand in the south-western corner of the room and wait for both Kree'arra and [[Flight Kilisa]], the melee bodyguard, to close in on you. <br/>
When both are in position, start throwing chinchompas at Flight Kilisa; the chinchompas will almost always hit her due to her lower [[Defence]], and the AoE damage will hit Kree'arra.

