Tbow / Bowfa=

The [[Twisted Bow]] and [[Bow of Faerdhinen]] are both viable methods for killing Kree'arra. While weaker than [[Black Chinchompa]]s, they're much cheaper to use and less click intensive.<br>
Twisted Bow is stronger than the Bow of Faerdhinen if the player has [[Masori armour set (f)|Masori armour (f)]] and [[Dragon arrow]]s—if missing two of those three items, the Bow of Faerdhinen with [[Crystal armour]] is stronger.<br>
Players should stand under Kree'arra after each hit to minimise the amount of attacks Kree'arra can use against the player, especially if using a Twisted Bow as its attack speed is slower than Bow of Faerdhinen

